</table>
</br></br>
</p>

@BGRND{{}}
<p>
@KJ{{part}}@HI{{karu}} involves a process of "figuring out" or processing information. Here it differs from
@KJ{{know}}@HI{{ru}}, which means "to obtain information from an external source".

